-- Copper Advances 0.5% to $6,717 a Metric Ton on the London Metal Exchange
-- Dan Weeks
-- 2010-07-14T08:05:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/copper-advances-0-5-to-6-717-a-metric-ton-on-the-london-metal-exchange.html

          
          
             Copper for three-month delivery rose
0.5 percent to $6,717 a metric ton on the London Metal Exchange.  
          
          


  


        